{"tid":28636,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大私家醫院動土　2020年啟用","createTime":"2016-12-08T05:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T06:37:04.000Z","uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f664241c43816b13ffaf39f751945cdd53e5e025","tid":28636,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:26:19.000Z","msg":"&quot;獲政府貸款50億元興建、本港首間非牟利的私家教學醫院「中文大學醫院」提供約600張病床，預計2020年第2季正式投入服務。該院今日（8日）舉行動土儀式， 食物及衞生局局長高永文等官員出席主禮。<br />\n<br />\n高永文致辭時表示，中大醫院主要服務香港人，2020年啟用初期預計提供90張病床，2026年可提供516張病床。此外，該院承諾每年接收公立醫院1.7萬宗門診個案及6,600宗日間手術，紓緩公院服務壓力。獲轉介的合資格市民，只需付公院收費。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張美蘭（2016年12月8日）。中大私家醫院動土　2020年啟用　市民經轉介入住只需付公院費用。香港01。<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/58714/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%8B%95%E5%9C%9F-2020%E5%B9%B4%E5%95%9F%E7%94%A8-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%B6%93%E8%BD%89%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E4%BD%8F%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E4%BB%98%E5%85%AC%E9%99%A2%E8%B2%BB%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F58714%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%259C%259F-2020%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2595%259F%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25B6%2593%25E8%25BD%2589%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%258F%25AA%25E9%259C%2580%25E4%25BB%2598%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E7%2594%25A8&d=6SNwFKqVviYZE5habXOENQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=28b2ac32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/58714/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%8B%95%E5%9C%9F-2020%E5%B9%B4%E5%95%9F%E7%94%A8-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%B6%93%E8%BD%89%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E4%BD%8F%E5%8F%AA%E9%9C%80%E4%BB%98%E5%85%AC%E9%99%A2%E8%B2%BB%E7%94%A8</a>"},{"pid":"b1b19b0804c8dc9ef1168bb0d12b6a237a602a88","tid":28636,"uid":40165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:28:22.000Z","msg